  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 350 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a blender, puree the green chilli, coconut milk, and honey until smooth.",
    "In a large bowl, combine the torn bread, pistachio, cardamom powder, and rose water.",
    "Pour the green chilli mixture over the bread mixture and stir until well combined.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a salt block vessel and bake for 25 minutes.",
    "Remove from the oven and let cool for 10 minutes.",
    "Serve warm and enjoy."
